What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, Prof. Duncan is great, and you probably have an equal great professor that you're doing research with. Be prepared to spend>10 hrs a week in lab. Only a short midterm report and final presentation required.
Do it if you need to do research for credit.

If you want to get some experience of research before the senior project take this class. Also if you just enjoy research and would like to have more experience in it before going to grad school or med school.
